---

---
<section id="experience" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-16 md:mb-24 lg:mb-36 lg:scroll-mt-24">
    <div class="mb-6">
        <h2 class="section-anchor text-md font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-900">
            Experience
        </h2>
        <div class="mt-3 h-px w-full bg-slate-400"></div>
    </div>

    <div>
        <ol class="space-y-12">
            <!-- IEEE -->
            <li class="relative grid pb-1 sm:grid-cols-8 sm:gap-8 md:gap-4">
                <div class="absolute -inset-x-4 -inset-y-4 z-0 hidden rounded-md lg:-inset-x-6 lg:block"></div>

                <header
                        class="z-10 mb-2 mt-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500 sm:col-span-2"
                        aria-label="2026 to Present"
                >
                    2026 — Present
                </header>

                <div class="z-10 sm:col-span-6">
                    <h3 class="font-medium leading-snug text-slate-900">
                        <div>
                            <a
                                    class="inline-flex items-baseline font-medium leading-tight text-slate-900 hover:text-teal-700 focus-visible:text-teal-700 group/link text-base"
                                    aria-label="IEEE Computer Society Student Chapter"
                            >
                                <span class="absolute -inset-x-4 -inset-y-2.5 hidden rounded md:-inset-x-6 md:-inset-y-4 lg:block"></span>
                                <span>Technical Volunteer · IEEE Computer Society Student Chapter</span>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </h3>

                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-normal text-slate-600">
                        Contributing to technical initiatives, collaborative engineering activities, and
                        professional development within the university technology community while strengthening
                        my backend and software architecture foundations.
                    </p>

                    <ul class="mt-2 flex flex-wrap gap-2" aria-label="Focus areas">
                        <li><span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-teal-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium leading-5 text-teal-700">Backend Development</span></li>
                        <li><span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-teal-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium leading-5 text-teal-700">Software Architecture</span></li>
                        <li><span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-teal-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium leading-5 text-teal-700">Community Collaboration</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>

            <!-- DISOFT -->
            <li class="relative grid pb-1 sm:grid-cols-8 sm:gap-8 md:gap-4">
                <div class="absolute -inset-x-4 -inset-y-4 z-0 hidden rounded-md lg:-inset-x-6 lg:block"></div>

                <header
                        class="z-10 mb-2 mt-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500 sm:col-span-2"
                        aria-label="November 2024 to May 2025"
                >
                    Nov 2024 — May 2025
                </header>

                <div class="z-10 sm:col-span-6">
                    <h3 class="font-medium leading-snug text-slate-900">
                        <div>
                            <a
                                    class="inline-flex items-baseline font-medium leading-tight text-slate-900 hover:text-teal-700 focus-visible:text-teal-700 group/link text-base"
                                    aria-label="Technical Support Intern at DISOFT SAC"
                            >
                                <span class="absolute -inset-x-4 -inset-y-2.5 hidden rounded md:-inset-x-6 md:-inset-y-4 lg:block"></span>
                                <span>Technical Support Intern · DISOFT SAC</span>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </h3>

                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-normal text-slate-600">
                        Supported clients in the use of a SaaS platform by identifying system issues, validating reports,
                        reporting bugs, and performing database-level adjustments when required. Contributed to improving
                        data accuracy, user experience, and overall system stability.
                    </p>

                    <ul class="mt-2 flex flex-wrap gap-2" aria-label="Technologies used">
                        <li><span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-teal-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium leading-5 text-teal-700">SaaS Support</span></li>
                        <li><span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-teal-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium leading-5 text-teal-700">Bug Tracking</span></li>
                        <li><span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-teal-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium leading-5 text-teal-700">Report Validation</span></li>
                        <li><span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-teal-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium leading-5 text-teal-700">Database Operations</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </div>
</section>
